ALGORITHM FOR THE SPLITTER 
1- count the words
2- allocat1 spae in memory with the number of words
3- iterate the string until finding a char
4- calls a function to know the length of the word by reaching space or null terminator
5- allocates space for the word 
6- init the word in each iteration until reaching the coming space and so on
7- repeat from step 3 until reaching the null byte
